msgstr "清除跳轉歷史記錄？"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:395
#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:707
msgid "Links"
msgstr "連結"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:398
msgid "Tap to follow links"
msgstr "點擊以前往連結"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:406
msgid "Tap on links to follow them."
msgstr "點擊連結以開啟。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:409
msgid "Ignore external links on tap"
msgstr "點擊時忽略外部連結"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:419
msgid ""
"Ignore taps on external links. Useful with Wikipedia EPUBs to make page turning easier.\n"
"You can still follow them from the dictionary window or the selection menu after holding on them."
msgstr ""
"忽略對外部連結的點擊事件，這在瀏覽維基百科時會更容易。\n"
"您仍可藉由長按後出現的字典視窗使用這些連結。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:426
msgid "Swipe to go back"
msgstr "滑動後返回跳轉前的位置"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:435
msgid ""
"Swipe to the right to go back to the previous location after you have "
"followed a link. When the location stack is empty, swiping to the right "
"takes you to the previous page."
msgstr "向右滑動回到上一次的位置。當位置不存在時，向右滑動將前往上一頁。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:439
msgid "Swipe to follow nearest link"
msgstr "滑動後前往最靠近手勢的連結"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:448
msgid ""
"Swipe to the left to follow the link nearest to where you started the swipe."
" This is useful when a small font is used and tapping on small links is "
"tedious."
msgstr "向左滑動來開啟距離滑動起始點最近的連結。當文字很小導致連結很難點的時候，這功能會非常有幫助。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:452
msgid "Ignore external links on swipe"
msgstr "滑動時忽略外部連結"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:462
msgid ""
"Ignore external links near swipe. Useful with Wikipedia EPUBs to follow only footnotes with swipe.\n"
"You can still follow external links from the dictionary window or the selection menu after holding on them."
msgstr ""
"忽略滑動附近的外部連結。這在瀏覽維基百科 EPUB，滑動只前往腳註時會更容易。\n"
"您仍可藉由長按後出現的字典視窗或選擇選單使用這些連結。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:469
msgid "Swipe to jump to latest bookmark"
msgstr "滑動後前往最新的書籤"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:478
msgid ""
"Swipe to the left to go the most recently bookmarked page.\n"
"This can be useful to quickly swipe back and forth between what you are reading and some reference page (for example notes, a map or a characters list).\n"
"If any of the other Swipe to follow link options is enabled, this will work only when the current page contains no link."
msgstr ""
"向左滑動前往上一次被書籤標注的頁面。\n"
"這可以被用在快速向前向後掃描某些參考頁上（例如筆記、地圖或人物列表）。\n"
"如果有任何一項「滑動後前往連結」選項是啟用的，則此功能僅適用於目前頁面中不包含任何連結。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:494
msgid "Allow larger tap area around links"
msgstr "允許連結周圍有更大的碰觸區"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:504
msgid ""
"Extends the tap area around internal links. Useful with a small font where "
"tapping on small footnote links may be tedious."
msgstr "擴張內部連結周圍的觸碰區域。當點擊使用小字型的腳註時，或可以免去一些冗長無趣的嘗試。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:508
msgid "Show footnotes in popup"
msgstr "將腳註顯示在彈窗中"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:520
msgid ""
"Show internal link target content in a footnote popup when it looks like it might be a footnote, instead of following the link.\n"
"\n"
"Note that depending on the book quality, footnote detection may not always work correctly.\n"
"The footnote content may be empty, truncated, or include other footnotes.\n"
"\n"
"From the footnote popup, you can jump to the footnote location in the book by swiping to the left."
msgstr ""
"當內部連結看起來像是腳註時，將其顯示在腳註彈窗中，而非前往該連結位置。\n"
"\n"
"注意，腳註偵測功能不見得能總是正確運作，這取決於書籍品質如何。\n"
"腳註的內容可能為空，或是被截斷，或包含其他腳註。\n"
"\n"
"在腳註彈窗中，您可以透過向左滑動，直接前往腳註於書籍中所在的位置。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:531
msgid "Footnote popup settings"
msgstr "腳註彈出設定"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:536
msgid "Show more links as footnotes"
msgstr "將更多連結視為腳註"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:549
msgid "Loosen footnote detection rules to show more links as footnotes."
msgstr "放寬腳註偵測規則以將更多連結視為腳註。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:554
msgid "Use book font as popup font"
msgstr "將書籍字型用作彈窗字型"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:566
msgid ""
"Display the footnote popup text with the font set as the document font (the "
"book text may still render with a different font if the book uses embedded "
"fonts)."
msgstr "將腳註彈出文本的字型設定為文件字型（如果文件使用了嵌入式字型，書本文本仍可能以不同字型呈現）。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:570
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:592
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:621
msgid "Set footnote popup font size"
msgstr "設定註解在彈出視窗裡的字型大小"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:591
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:620
msgid "Set font size"
msgstr "設定字型大小"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:594
msgid ""
"The footnote popup font can adjust to the font size you've set for the "
"document, but you can specify here a fixed absolute font size to be used "
"instead."
msgstr "腳註彈出視窗內的文字尺寸會調整為你指定的文件字型大小，但是您可以在這裡指定要使用的固定絕對字型大小。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:604
msgid "Set a relative font size instead"
msgstr "設定相對字型大小"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:622
msgid ""
"The footnote popup font adjusts to the font size you've set for the document.\n"
"You can specify here how much smaller or larger it should be relative to the document font size.\n"
"A negative value will make it smaller, while a positive one will make it larger.\n"
"The recommended value is -2."
msgstr ""
"腳註彈出視窗內的文字尺寸會調整為你指定的文件字型大小。\n"
"你可以在這裡指定腳註的字型大小要比正文的小多少或大多少。\n"
"負數值讓腳註的字型比較小，正數值讓腳註的字型比較大。\n"
"建議的數值是 -2。"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:634
msgid "Set an absolute font size instead"
msgstr "設定絕對字型大小"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:650
msgid ""
"The footnote popup font adjusts to the font size you've set for the document.\n"
"This allows you to specify how much smaller or larger it should be relative to the document font size."
msgstr ""
"腳註彈出視窗內的文字尺寸會調整為你指定的文件字型大小。\n"
"這可以讓你指定腳註相對於正文，字型大小要小多少或大多少。"

