#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:110
msgid "Two Columns"
msgstr "兩欄"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:133
msgid ""
"Render the document on half the screen width and display two pages at once with a single page number. This makes it look like two columns.\n"
"This is disabled in scroll mode. Switching from page mode with two columns to scroll mode will cause the document to be re-rendered."
msgstr ""
"以一半的螢幕寬度繪製文件並在一頁中同時顯示兩個頁面。這使得它看起來像兩欄。\n"
"此行為在捲動模式會被停用。從兩欄的頁面模式切換到捲動模式會重新繪製文件。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:144
msgid "L/R Margins"
msgstr "左/右邊距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:177
msgid "Left/Right Margins"
msgstr "左/右邊距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:191
msgid "Sync T/B Margins"
msgstr "同步上/下邊距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:200
msgid ""
"Keep top and bottom margins synchronized.\n"
"- 'off' allows different top and bottom margins.\n"
"- 'on' keeps top and bottom margins locked, ensuring text is vertically centered in the page.\n"
"\n"
"In the top menu → Settings → Status bar, you can choose whether the bottom margin applies from the bottom of the screen, or from above the status bar."
msgstr ""
"讓上和下邊距保持同步。\n"
"- 「關閉」 允許不同的上和下邊距。\n"
"- 「開啟」 鎖定上和下邊距，確保文字在頁面中垂直置中。\n"
"\n"
"在頂部選單 → 設定 → 狀態列中，您可以選擇是從螢幕底部還是從狀態列上方套用下邊距。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:209
#: plugins/simpleui.koplugin/sui_homescreen.lua:2409
msgid "Top Margin"
msgstr "上邊距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:246 frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:302
msgid "Top/Bottom Margins"
msgstr "上/下邊距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:264
#: plugins/simpleui.koplugin/sui_menu.lua:1866
#: plugins/simpleui.koplugin/sui_menu.lua:1868
msgid "Bottom Margin"
msgstr "底部邊距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:297
msgid ""
"In the top menu → Settings → Status bar, you can choose whether the bottom "
"margin applies from the bottom of the screen, or from above the status bar."
msgstr "在頂部選單 → 設定 → 狀態列中，您可以選擇是從螢幕底部還是從狀態列上方套用下邊距。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:325 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:380
msgid "View Mode"
msgstr "檢視模式"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:326 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:381
msgid "continuous"
msgstr "連續"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:334
msgid ""
"- 'page' mode splits the text into pages, at the most acceptable places (page numbers and the number of pages may change when you change fonts, margins, styles, etc.).\n"
"- 'continuous' mode allows you to scroll the text like you would in a web browser (the 'Page Overlap' setting is only available in this mode)."
msgstr ""
"- 「頁面」模式將文字於適當的位置切分為多頁（具體頁碼與頁數可能會因為字型、邊距、樣式等原因而改變）。\n"
"- 「連續」模式允許您像網頁瀏覽器一樣捲動文字（「頁面重疊」設定只有在這個模式下有效）。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:340
msgid "Render Mode"
msgstr "繪製模式"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:342
msgid "legacy"
msgstr "傳統"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:343
msgid "flat"
msgstr "平坦"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:344
msgid "book"
msgstr "書籍"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:345
msgid "web"
msgstr "網頁"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:353
msgid ""
"- 'legacy' uses original CR3 block rendering code.\n"
"- 'flat' ensures flat rendering with collapsing margins and accurate page breaks.\n"
"- 'book' additionally allows floats, but limits style support to avoid blank spaces and overflows.\n"
"- 'web' renders as web browsers do, allowing negative margins and possible page overflow."
msgstr ""
"- 「傳統」使用原有的 CR3 區塊繪製代碼。\n"
"- 「平坦」使用平坦繪製，在繪製時折疊邊距並提供準確的頁面分頁。\n"
"- 「書籍」另外允許浮動，但是會限制樣式支援，以避免空白和溢出。\n"
"- 「網頁」將使用和網頁瀏覽器相同的繪製，允許負邊距和可能的頁面溢出。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:362
msgid "Zoom (dpi)"
msgstr "縮放 (dpi)"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:366
msgctxt "Resolution"
msgid "dpi"
msgstr "dpi"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:374
msgid ""
"Sets the DPI used to scale absolute CSS units and images:\n"
"- off: ignore absolute units (old engine behavior).\n"
"- 96¹’¹: at 96 DPI, 1 CSS pixel = 1 screen pixel and images are rendered at their original dimensions.\n"
"- other values scale CSS absolute units and images by a factor (300 DPI = x3, 48 DPI = x0.5)\n"
"Using your device's actual DPI will ensure 1 cm in CSS actually translates to 1 cm on screen.\n"
"Note that your selected font size is not affected by this setting."
msgstr ""
"設定所使用的 DPI 來縮放 CSS 絕對單位與圖片：\n"
"- 關閉：忽略絕對單位（舊引擎行為）\n"
"- 96¹’¹：在 96 DPI 時，1 CSS 像素點 = 1 螢幕像素點，此時圖片會被算繪成它原始的長寬大小。\n"
"- 其他數值將依其縮放因子縮放 CSS 絕對單位與圖片大小 (300 DPI = x3, 48 DPI = x0.5)\n"
"使用您裝置真實的 DPI 將能確保 CSS 中的 1 公分能夠實際對應到螢幕上的一公分。\n"
"注意，您選擇的字型大小不會受到本項設定的影響。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:392 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:431
msgid "Line Spacing"
msgstr "行間距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:465 frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:468
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:502 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:505
msgid "decrease"
msgstr "減少"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:465 frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:468
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:502 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:505
msgid "increase"
msgstr "增加"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:496
msgid "Word Spacing"
msgstr "文字間距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:500
msgid "Word spacing"
msgstr "文字間距"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:502
msgid ""
"Set word spacing percentages:\n"
"- how much to scale the width of each space character from its regular width,\n"
"- by how much some of them can then be reduced to make more words fit on a line."
msgstr ""
"設定文字間距百分比：\n"
"- 設定每個空格字元縮放的寬度，\n"
"- 以及需要使更多文字排在同一行時空格字元最小縮放比例。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:506
msgid "Scaling"
msgstr "縮放比例"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:511
msgid "Reduction"
msgstr "縮減"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:520
msgctxt "Word spacing"
msgid "small"
msgstr "小"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:521
msgctxt "Word spacing"
msgid "medium"
msgstr "中"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:522
msgctxt "Word spacing"
msgid "large"
msgstr "大"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:539
msgid ""
"Tells the rendering engine by how much to scale the width of each 'space' "
"character in the text from its regular width, and by how much it can "
"additionally reduce them to make more words fit on a line (100% means no "
"reduction)."
msgstr "告訴繪製引擎縮放空白字元寬度的程度，以及空白字元可額外減少的寬度來使更多文字在同一行（100% 代表不縮放）。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:549
msgid "Word Expansion"
msgstr "字母間間隙"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:558
msgid "Max word expansion"
msgstr "最大字母間間隙"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:560
msgid "Set max word expansion as a percentage of the font size."
msgstr "將最大單詞擴充套件設定為字型大小的百分比。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:564
msgid "CJK scaling"
msgstr "CJK 縮放比"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:569
msgctxt "Word expansion"
msgid "none"
msgstr "無"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:570
msgctxt "Word expansion"
msgid "some"
msgstr "一些"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:571
msgctxt "Word expansion"
msgid "more"
msgstr "更多"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:588
msgid ""
"On justified lines having too wide spaces, allow distributing the excessive "
"space into words by expanding them with letter spacing. This sets the max "
"allowed letter spacing as a % of the font size."
msgstr "當左右對齊空格太寬時，允許將多餘的空白分散至所有單字的字母間。此設定控制字母間空白相對於字型大小的最大百分比。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:614
msgid "CJK width scaling"
msgstr "CJK 字元間距縮放"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:616
msgid ""
"Increase the width of all CJK (Chinese, Japanese, Korean) characters by this"
" percentage. This has the effect of adding space between these glyphs, and "
"might make them easier to distinguish to some readers."
msgstr "按此百分比增加所有中日韓（CJK）字元的寬度。這樣做的效果是在這些字形之間增加空間，可能會使一些讀者更容易區分它們。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:620
msgid "Word expansion"
msgstr "字母間隙"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:632 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:567
msgid "Contrast"
msgstr "對比"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:712
msgid "Font Weight"
msgstr "字型粗細"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:727
msgid ""
"Set the font weight delta from \"regular\" to apply to all fonts.\n"
"\n"
"- 0 will use the \"Regular (400)\" variation of a font.\n"
"- +1 will use the \"Medium (500)\" variation of a font if available.\n"
"- +3 will use the \"Bold (700)\" variation of a font if available.\n"
"If a font variation is not available, as well as for fractional adjustments, it will be synthesized from the nearest available weight."
msgstr ""
"設定來自“常規”的字重 delta 來應用到所有字型。\n"
"\n"
"- 0 將使用字型的 \"Regular (400)\" 變體。\n"
"- +1 將使用字型的 \"Medium (500)\" 變體，如果有的話。\n"
"- +3 將使用字型的 \"Bold (700)\" 變體, 如果有的話。\n"
"如果一個字型變體不可用，也無法進行部分調整，將從最接近的可用字重進行合成。"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:741
msgid "The default font '%1' provides the following weight classes: %2."
msgstr "預設字型「%1」提供下列字重類別：%2。"

