#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:168
msgid ""
"Disallow taps or keyboard presses being sent to the UI elements before they are showing up.\n"
"E-ink screens are slow and take noticeable time to update the content. Users may feel laggy, tap the screen or press the keyboard multiple times, and cause the following actions to interact with the unshown UI elements and trigger unexpected actions.\n"
"This feature decides if a user action is expected or caused by the delay of screen refreshing, and drops the unexpected ones.\n"
"It's highly suggested keeping this configuration enabled unless you feel the UI interactions are less responsive."
msgstr ""
"不允許在 UI 元素顯示之前向其發送點擊或鍵盤按鍵。\n"
"電子墨水屏較慢，需要明顯的時間來更新內容。使用者可能會感到延遲，多次點擊屏幕或按鍵盤，從起後續操作與未顯示的 UI 元素互動並觸發意外操作。\n"
"此功能判定使用者操作是預期的還是由於屏幕重新整理延遲引起的，並丟棄意外的操作。\n"
"強烈建議保持此設定啟用，除非您覺得 UI 互動響應變慢。"

