#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:8
msgid "About fully refreshing screens"
msgstr "關於全螢幕重新整理"

#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:13
msgid ""
"Showing a new content on an E-ink screen usually does not fully clear the previous content and leaves some blur. It may be referred as E-ink shadow or ghosting.\n"
"The blur needs a full refresh to be cleared cleanly. But a full refresh can be slow and trigger a flicker.\n"
"KOReader allows users deciding the frequence of the full refresh, i.e. more full refreshes for better display quality or less full refreshes for responsiveness.\n"
"Usually you do not to adjust this configuration, the balanced setting should be good enough for most of the use cases."
msgstr ""
"在電子墨水屏上顯示新內容通常不會完全清除先前內容，並會留下一些模糊。這可能被稱為電子墨水屏殘影或鬼影。\n"
"模糊需要全螢幕重新整理才能清除乾淨。但全螢幕重新整理可能較慢並觸發閃爍。\n"
"KOReader 允許使用者決定全螢幕重新整理的頻率，即較多的全螢幕重新整理以獲得更好的顯示品質，或較少以提高響應速度。\n"
"通常您不需要調整此設定，平衡的設定對大多數使用場景都足夠好。"

#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:19
msgid "Never automatically fully refresh screen"
msgstr "從不自動全螢幕重新整理"

#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:21
msgid ""
"The full refresh will happen only when showing an image, moving to next "
"chapter or opening another book."
msgstr "全螢幕重新整理僅在顯示圖像、跳轉到下一章或開啟另一本書時發生。"

#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:32
msgid "Low full refresh rate for better responsiveness"
msgstr "低全螢幕重新整理率以獲得更好的響應速度"

#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:42
msgid "Balance between responsiveness and quality"
msgstr "響應速度和品質之間的平衡"

#: frontend/ui/elements/refresh_menu_table.lua:58
msgid "High full refresh rate for better display quality"
msgstr "高全螢幕重新整理率以獲得更好的顯示品質"

