#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:551
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:558
msgid "Text selection rate"
msgstr "文字選擇速度"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:559
msgid ""
"The rate is how often screen will be refreshed per second while selecting text.\n"
"Higher values mean faster screen updates, but also use more CPU."
msgstr ""
"該速度是在選擇文字時螢幕每隔幾秒重新整理一次。\n"
"更高的值意味著更快的螢幕更新，但也使用更多的 CPU。"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:568
msgctxt "Frequency"
msgid "Hz"
msgstr "赫茲"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:569
msgid "Set rate"
msgstr "設定速度"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:581
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:585
msgid "Tap interval"
msgstr "點擊間隔"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:587
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:616
msgid ""
"Any other taps made within this interval after a first tap will be considered accidental and ignored.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 0 (0 seconds) to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"第一次點按之後的這段時間內，任何其他相同動作都將被視為意外事件，並被忽略。\n"
"\n"
"間隔值以毫秒為單位，範圍從0(0秒)到2000(2秒)。"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:610
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:614
msgid "Tap interval on keyboard"
msgstr "鍵盤點擊間隔"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:644
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:648
msgid "Double tap interval"
msgstr "雙擊間隔"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:650
msgid ""
"When double tap is enabled, this sets the time to wait for the second tap. A single tap will take at least this long to be detected.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"雙擊啟用時，這將設定等待第二次點選的時間。單個點選至少需要這麼長的時間才能被檢測到。\n"
"\n"
"間隔值以毫秒為單位，範圍從100(0.1秒)到2000(2秒)。"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:673
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:677
msgid "Two finger tap duration"
msgstr "兩根手指點擊間隔"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:679
msgid ""
"This sets the allowed duration of any of the two fingers touch/release for the combined event to be considered a two finger tap.\n"
"\n"
"The duration value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"這將設定任意兩指觸控/釋放的允許持續時間，使組合事件被認為是一個兩指點選。\n"
"\n"
"持續時間值以毫秒為單位，範圍從100(0.1秒)到2000(2秒)。"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:691
msgid "Set duration"
msgstr "設定持續時間"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:705
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:709
msgid "Long-press interval"
msgstr "長按間隔"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:711
msgid ""
"If a touch is not released in this interval, it is considered a long-press. On document text, single word selection will then be triggered.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"如果一個觸控沒有在這個間隔內釋放，它會被認為是長按。這會在文件文本上觸發選中單個單詞。\n"
"\n"
"間隔值以毫秒為單位，範圍從100(0.1秒)到2000(2秒)。"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:734
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:738
msgid "Swipe interval"
msgstr "滑動間隔"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:740
msgid ""
"This sets the maximum delay between the start and the end of a swipe for it to be considered a swipe. Above this interval, it's considered panning.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"設定從滑動開始到滑動結束之間的最大延遲。超過這個區間，該動作將被認為是拖拽。\n"
"\n"
"間隔值以毫秒為單位，範圍從 100 (0.1秒)到 2000 (2秒)。"

